><H2
>Name</H2
>FcConfigSetSysRoot&nbsp;--&nbsp;Set the system root directory</DIV
><DIV
CLASS="REFSYNOPSISDIV"
><A
NAME="AEN3404"
></A
><H2
>Synopsis</H2
><DIV
CLASS="FUNCSYNOPSIS"
><P
></P
><A
